<mxfile host="Electron" agent="Mozilla/5.0 (X11; Linux x86_64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) draw.io/29.0.3 Chrome/140.0.7339.249 Electron/38.7.0 Safari/537.36" version="29.0.3" pages="12">
  <diagram name="Product Service Class Diagram by Abdulwahab ADamson" id="fRL6FD9JQs9WDaBqlZ8T">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1195" dy="727" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="1654" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="PiptD506YynuU_DmixTl-1" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Product Service&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;Class Diagram&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;by Abdulwahab Adamson&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Date: 22nd March, 2026&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="40" y="40" width="240" height="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="1EiskbM_ylhq_rnkx_y1-1" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;Reflection&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;I chose to position the `ProductService` at the top-middle of the diagram because it is one of the most important components in the system. It serves as the central layer that coordinates interactions between other parts of the application.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;The `ProductService` manages the main entity (`Product`) and handles the associated Data Transfer Objects (DTOs). It contains the core business logic and ensures data flows correctly between layers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;It also interacts with other stereotypes such as repositories and DTOs to perform its operations. For example, it uses the repository to access and store data, and DTOs to transfer data between different layers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Placing the `ProductService` in the center makes its role clear as the main point of coordination between entities, repositories, and DTOs, and helps improve the readability of the diagram.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="40" y="964" width="880" height="170" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
